# CFA Module Data Files

## Exports

```js
export const LM## = { id, topic, topicName, title, subtitle, estimatedTime, weight,
  learningOutcomes, keyTerms, sections, formulaSheet }
export const LM##_ITEM_SETS = [ /* vignette + 4 MCQs */ ]
export const LM##_GLASSBOX = [ /* required for every new module */ ]
```

## Glassbox entry shape

```js
{ id, title, topic, question, answer, principle, steps: [{ text, formula }] }
```

- `principle` = first-principles sentence
- `steps` = transparent math; formulas are plain text for `.formula-box`
- Verify arithmetic before shipping

## Item-set shape

```js
{ id, title, vignette, questions: [{ id, question, options[4], answer /*0-3*/, solution, lo }] }
```

Solutions must be glassbox-style (steps + bold final answer), not one-liners.
